{
  "texts": [
    "Two approaches were followed while developing deep learning models.",
    "The first approach was pre-trained transfer learning models used for classification model development.",
    "In the second approach, a CNN-based model for classification was developed from scratch.",
    "The effect of image type on classification accuracy was studied as input to network colour images, grayscale images, and background-removed images were used.",
    "The accuracy of the two models was expressed in terms of the F1 score."
  ]
}